posting_body: ['Contact info:', 'Toni Hill | The Apartment Resource |', 'show contact info', '1Br/1BA Apartment', 'Flying Cloud Dr, Eden Prairie, MN', '$1400/mo', 'KEY FEATURES', 'Sq Footage:', '780 sqft.', 'Bedrooms:', '1', 'Bathrooms:', '1', 'Parking:', 'Parking: $50/Garage Parking', 'Lease Duration:', '12 Months', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Pets Policy:', 'Dogs & Cats OK (Spayed/Neutered)', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Property Type:', 'Apartment', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Offering large one and two-bedroom apartments with modernized interiors and stylish comfort.', 'The remodeled Clubhouse and amenity spaces enhance a balanced stylish lifestyle.', 'Indoor and outdoor pools, tennis and basketball courts, dog park, kids room, and other amenities are tailored to lounge, play, or entertain- in solitude, or with friends and family.', 'A silent picturesque backdrop of forest and trail access makes this a great location, in the most convenient and loved area of Eden Prairie.', 'Join us for a tour, and reserve your apartment today!', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Prices and availability are subject to change.', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES', 'Indoor Basketball Court', 'Business Center', 'Clubhouse', 'Off-leash Dog Park', 'Nature/Fitness Trails', 'Pet Friendly Community', 'Playground', 'Elevator', 'Fitness Center', 'Heated Underground Garage', 'On-Site Maintenance', 'On-Site Management', 'Heated Indoor and Outdoor Pools', 'Recreation Room', 'Sauna', 'Sundeck', 'Tennis Court', 'BBQ/Picnic Area', 'Smoke Free', 'APARTMENT AMENITIES', 'Patio/Balcony', 'Full-size Washer and Dryer', 'Large Walk-in Closets', 'Large, Walk-in Rentable Storage Rooms', 'Air Conditioner', 'Bay Windows*', 'Microwave', 'In-unit Storage*', 'Dishwasher', 'Linen Closet*', 'Private Balcony/Patio*', 'Contact info:', 'Toni Hill', 'The Apartment Resource', 'show contact info']
